## Alternative: Whitelabel API

If Onramp.money supports API access (check docs):

```typescript
// More integrated approach
async function buyUSDCWithOnramp(amount: string) {
    const response = await fetch('https://api.onramp.money/v1/orders', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: {
            'Authorization': `Bearer ${process.env.ONRAMP_API_KEY}`,
            'Content-Type': 'application/json'
        },
        body: JSON.stringify({
            fiat_amount: amount,
            fiat_currency: 'INR',
            crypto_currency: 'USDC',
            network: 'STELLAR',
            wallet_address: userAddress,
            payment_method: 'UPI'
        })
    })
    
    const order = await response.json()
    return order
}
```

